{"title":"「2017 山东二轮集训 Day6」汇合","time_limit":2000,"memory_limit":4,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/6115#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=6115","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/6115/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/6115/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/6115"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"有 $ n $ 个人，他们构成了一颗有根树，每个人只能往他的父亲走，现在有 $ m $ 个询问，每次询问 A 和 B 想要汇合的话，最近汇点是哪一个。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行两个正整数 $ n $。  \r\n接下来 $ n - 1 $ 行每行一个正整数，依次表示点 $ 2 \\sim n $ 的父亲，保证每个点的父亲小于它本身。  \r\n接下来 $ m $ 行每行两个数表示一个询问。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对每个询问单独输出一行表示答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n5 2\r\n1\r\n1\r\n2\r\n2\r\n3 5\r\n4 5\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n1\r\n2\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$ n \\leq 900000, m \\leq 100000 $"}]}